data.description: Welcome to 3641 Kensley Drive, a charming 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom house located in the highly desirable Carlton Square community of Inglewood. This two-story home offers a comfortable and secure living experience with its gated entrance and security features.  Inside, you'll find a spacious floor plan spanning 1467 square feet, featuring dual pane windows and doors that invite plenty of natural light. The central heat and air conditioning ensure year-round comfort, while the cozy fireplace adds warmth during those colder winter nights.  The property offers convenient amenities such as a gym, 2 pools, tennis court, half basketball court, and playground, perfect for staying active and entertaining guests. With a 2-car garage and additional parking spaces available, you'll never have to worry about finding parking.  Outside, the backyard provides a private retreat where you can relax and enjoy the California sun. Located right across from SoFi Stadium and near schools, parks, and major freeways, this home offers easy access to everything Inglewood has to offer. Don't miss your chance to make this delightful house your new home!!!!
